OL,4,G0405FDrop The Dead Donkey
OL,5,     GAfter a sudden death at
OL,6,     GGlobeLink, Gus goes into exercise
OL,7,     Goverdrive to try to defer his own
OL,8,     Gdemise. Meanwhile, George tries
OL,9,     Ghis hand at acting; and Damien
OL,10,     Ghas trouble with his Porsche.
OL,11,G0430FStereo Underground
OL,12,     GRichard Latto presents
OL,13,     Galternative anthems from a music
OL,14,     Gcommunity with attitude.
OL,15,G0530FJack Hargreaves' Old Country
OL,16,     GWith construction of his road
OL,17,     Gcart complete, Jack arranges for
OL,18,     Git to be decorated. Then on the
OL,19,     Gsite of a hill fort in Dorset he
OL,20,     Gspots many different species of
OL,21,     Gbutterfly.
